# Incident Table Example

The Incident table stores records related to incidents reported by users.

## Example Record

| Field | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Number | INC0010001 |
| Caller | John Doe |
| Priority | High |
| State | New |
| Short Description | Unable to access email |

## Observation

- Each row is a record.
- Each column is a field.
- The Incident table inherits from the Task table.
